name: A Universal Income Spheric Scheme
description: *The best thing about free money is that you can learn a lot of stuff from it before you start investing it. Many people spend hundreds of dollars on anything that shows up on a spreadsheet or website. In my opinion this is the greatest thing about online money. *This means that there is nothing more difficult or expensive to find money for (nor really any), but instead you have a whole array of activities available on your computer that you can quickly spend.
